    <p>The slim format affects nicotine release kinetics. Smaller surface area means slightly faster release—typically reaching peak blood levels within 10–15 minutes rather than 15–20 minutes. This makes them ideal for <a href="/blog/best-nicotine-pouches-for-beginners-2026">beginners</a> and users with lighter tolerance.</p>
    <p>With <strong>672 out of 731 products (92%) in our catalogue as slim format</strong>, manufacturers and retailers have aligned on what works. Slim offers the sweet spot between discretion, comfort, and effectiveness.</p>

