    <h3>Is slim format suitable for beginners?</h3>
    <p>Absolutely. Start with a light-strength slim pouch (4–6mg). The slim format's faster nicotine release and smaller size make it ideal for newcomers.</p>

    <h3>What's the difference between slim and mini pouches?</h3>
